WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 27=

01:48.710 --> 01:54.150
ظآزBetween black and white,
ripples crossedظآز

01:54.330 --> 01:58.660
ظآزLight encountered shadowظآز

02:00.030 --> 02:05.420
ظآزIt pierced the darkness and the timeظآز

02:05.650 --> 02:09.590
ظآزThe unbreakable fateظآز

02:11.360 --> 02:13.250
ظآزSuddenly crackedظآز

02:16.510 --> 02:17.350
We meet again,

02:18.740 --> 02:19.580
Foxy.

02:19.660 --> 02:22.820
ظآزListen, all sounds are roaringظآز

02:22.820 --> 02:25.350
ظآزAs cold ice turns into tidesظآز

02:25.350 --> 02:30.870
ظآزA century's loneliness melts dreamsظآز

02:30.870 --> 02:34.110
ظآزFollowing fate's guidanceظآز

02:34.110 --> 02:38.970
ظآزBy fate, our moments were exchangedظآز

02:39.310 --> 02:42.330
ظآزThe heart wakes up all of a suddenظآز

02:42.350 --> 02:43.420
(I must have lost my mind.)

02:44.900 --> 02:46.020
(How could she be here?)

03:04.270 --> 03:05.110
What a surprise

03:05.670 --> 03:07.270
to see General Duan here.

03:09.550 --> 03:10.390
What a coincidence.

03:10.900 --> 03:12.110
Mr. Fang is here too.

03:17.180 --> 03:18.230
I won't disturb you two.

03:18.550 --> 03:19.740
I'll take my leave now.

03:22.860 --> 03:23.700
It seems

03:24.420 --> 03:25.390
that you've taken

03:25.700 --> 03:26.786
a liking

03:26.797 --> 03:27.740
to Mr. Wang's daughter.

03:29.420 --> 03:30.550
Who's interested

03:31.420 --> 03:32.510
in whom I favor,

03:33.460 --> 03:34.460
you

03:34.460 --> 03:35.300
or the Duke?

03:35.510 --> 03:36.350
What do you think?

03:37.350 --> 03:38.190
General Duan.

03:44.550 --> 03:45.390
Fang Xianye,

03:45.580 --> 03:46.700
I knew you meant no good.

03:47.070 --> 03:47.950
You want to steal

03:47.950 --> 03:48.790
Xu's date.

03:49.420 --> 03:51.020
You, come with me.

03:51.860 --> 03:53.180
Xu, go after her.

03:53.510 --> 03:54.350
Go on.

03:55.580 --> 03:56.420
Come here.

04:29.990 --> 04:30.830
Fang Xianye,

04:31.150 --> 04:32.620
don't you dare hinder Xu.

04:41.590 --> 04:42.430
Miss Duan,

04:42.620 --> 04:43.790
neither of them is wed.

04:44.060 --> 04:45.060
How am I in the way?

04:45.620 --> 04:46.550
Besides, Miss Wang

04:46.860 --> 04:48.470
may not favor Mr. Duan.

04:49.260 --> 04:50.100
Xu's affairs

04:50.110 --> 04:51.230
are not yours to meddle in.

04:52.110 --> 04:53.790
Xu is far better than you.

04:54.230 --> 04:55.620
Even if Suyi rejects Xu,

04:55.620 --> 04:56.820
she'd never choose you.

04:57.060 --> 04:58.550
Nothing is settled yet.

04:59.180 --> 05:00.990
Why speak with such certainty?

05:01.550 --> 05:02.390
I...

05:05.560 --> 05:06.420
Anyway,

05:06.420 --> 05:07.740
stop hindering Xu.

05:11.030 --> 05:11.870
Do not be upset.

05:12.420 --> 05:13.260
I won't disturb

05:13.420 --> 05:14.550
your stroll

05:14.550 --> 05:15.390
in the garden.

05:15.590 --> 05:16.790
- Iظخ
- Goodbye.

05:20.060 --> 05:20.900
Wait.

05:23.620 --> 05:25.110
How do you know the Six-Petal Knot?

05:27.030 --> 05:28.860
Only Xu can tie that knot.

05:31.110 --> 05:32.350
Why are you so annoying,

05:32.710 --> 05:33.910
coping Xu in all things?

05:34.380 --> 05:36.180
You want his date and knot.

05:36.500 --> 05:37.710
I don't want to see you again.

05:46.940 --> 05:48.030
You do have a sharp memory.

06:00.470 --> 06:01.350
Little trinkets!

06:01.350 --> 06:03.300
Come look, come see.

06:12.150 --> 06:13.380
Weren't you at the banquet?

06:13.820 --> 06:14.820
Why are you back so soon?

06:15.670 --> 06:17.500
I did what my old man asked,

06:17.500 --> 06:18.340
and I left.

06:19.230 --> 06:20.070
Why are you here?

06:21.180 --> 06:22.020
I...

06:24.550 --> 06:25.620
I went to look for Xu.

06:26.180 --> 06:27.110
He went to the banquet,

06:27.550 --> 06:29.016
so I'll wait at Yuzao Pleasure House.

06:29.940 --> 06:31.060
Xu is still inside.

06:31.300 --> 06:32.500
Go wait for him. I'm leaving.

06:41.790 --> 06:42.910
Why are you following me?

06:43.060 --> 06:44.079
Aren't you waiting for Xu?

06:44.380 --> 06:45.220
He

06:45.710 --> 06:47.180
won't be out anytime soon.

06:47.470 --> 06:48.470
I'd better head back.

06:49.670 --> 06:50.670
Your home is that way.

06:55.500 --> 06:56.940
I can get back from this way too.

07:05.740 --> 07:06.910
How was today's banquet?

07:08.420 --> 07:09.260
Not much to speak of.

07:09.790 --> 07:11.470
Did you meet anyone

07:11.470 --> 07:12.310
or anything

07:12.550 --> 07:13.390
interesting there?

07:14.060 --> 07:14.900
No.

07:16.940 --> 07:18.150
It was terribly dull.

07:18.989 --> 07:20.529
Let's go drink at Yuzao Pleasure House.

07:21.110 --> 07:21.950
Sure.

07:22.320 --> 07:23.180
I heard they had

07:23.180 --> 07:24.710
a new batch of fine wine.

07:25.710 --> 07:26.860
With your capacity,

07:26.860 --> 07:27.700
you know the wine

07:27.710 --> 07:28.860
at Yuzao Pleasure House?

07:28.990 --> 07:30.260
I kept an eye out just for you.

07:31.060 --> 07:31.910
You're my good buddy.

07:32.300 --> 07:33.140
Come on.

07:34.590 --> 07:35.820
Move. Hurry up.

07:41.500 --> 07:42.340
- Zhou.
- Li.

07:42.490 --> 07:43.350
Zhao.

07:43.350 --> 07:44.190
Long time no see.

07:44.200 --> 07:45.050
Indeed.

07:45.500 --> 07:46.380
How have you been?

07:46.820 --> 07:47.670
Not bad.

07:47.680 --> 07:49.260
A few days ago, I read your prose.

07:50.860 --> 07:52.470
You flatter me.

08:42.780 --> 08:43.620
Great Ancestor,

08:44.020 --> 08:44.860
you're back.

08:45.350 --> 08:46.230
What did you find out?

08:46.740 --> 08:48.140
Today, at the banquet,

08:48.430 --> 08:49.780
I left marks on those

08:49.780 --> 08:50.620
with deep obsessions.

08:51.310 --> 08:52.590
Approach them

08:52.601 --> 08:53.620
as the Prophet to gather

08:54.430 --> 08:55.270
their obsessions.

08:57.740 --> 08:58.580
Yes.

08:59.310 --> 09:00.470
When you approach them,

09:00.470 --> 09:01.500
look into them.

09:02.660 --> 09:04.470
Song Xingyu will likely forge

09:04.780 --> 09:06.660
a pact with such people as before.

09:07.230 --> 09:08.710
If we find them,

09:09.740 --> 09:11.140
we may find Song Xingyu.

09:13.140 --> 09:14.190
Great Ancestor,

09:14.710 --> 09:16.260
good for you.

09:19.830 --> 09:20.670
Great Ancestor,

09:20.830 --> 09:21.830
did you see it today?

09:22.260 --> 09:23.310
Duan Xu was

09:23.710 --> 09:25.590
so attentive to that young lady.

09:26.190 --> 09:27.830
What was that young lady called again?

09:27.830 --> 09:28.670
Her name isظخ

09:32.430 --> 09:33.500
Great Ancestor,

09:35.020 --> 09:36.020
isn't this the life

09:36.020 --> 09:37.190
you wanted for him?

09:37.190 --> 09:38.780
Why take it out on me?

09:38.780 --> 09:40.310
Go do what you should do.

09:41.780 --> 09:43.260
Less talk about the rest.

09:45.430 --> 09:46.270
Yes.

10:14.140 --> 10:15.140
Xu, I'm coming in.

10:29.430 --> 10:30.270
Xu,

10:31.380 --> 10:33.070
from how you reacted today,

10:33.260 --> 10:34.660
have you taken to Wang Suyi?

10:36.990 --> 10:38.190
Can you help me meet her?

10:41.110 --> 10:42.660
Miss Wang and I

10:42.900 --> 10:44.260
do have some acquaintance.

10:44.590 --> 10:45.713
She often attends

10:45.724 --> 10:46.860
the Embroidery Society I run.

10:48.430 --> 10:50.310
I still owe her
a Suzhou-style embroidered fan.

10:50.620 --> 10:51.900
I'll deliver it tomorrow

10:51.900 --> 10:52.860
and ask her for you.

10:58.350 --> 10:59.830
As you asked,

10:59.830 --> 11:00.830
I'm here.

11:01.830 --> 11:02.670
Where are you?

11:03.140 --> 11:03.980
Great Ancestor,

11:04.350 --> 11:05.620
I am truly sorry.

11:06.500 --> 11:08.900
I have to wait for the medicine.

11:09.830 --> 11:11.260
Take a stroll. I'll come soon.

11:11.470 --> 11:13.070
How dare you make me wait?

11:13.780 --> 11:15.350
I am innocent too.

11:16.260 --> 11:17.140
It is Ziji's fault.

11:17.540 --> 11:19.353
If I skip the medicine,
she won't let me out.

11:20.620 --> 11:21.500
I'll be there at once.

11:21.990 --> 11:22.900
Great Ancestor, look.

11:23.350 --> 11:24.430
She's calling me again.

11:24.430 --> 11:25.270
I'm going now.

11:34.380 --> 11:35.220
Forget it.

11:35.950 --> 11:37.070
I'll count this as a day off.

11:38.900 --> 11:39.830
Here, hold it tight.

11:39.830 --> 11:40.670
Thanks.

11:50.190 --> 11:51.736
Miss, would you like a sugar figurine?

11:53.590 --> 11:54.430
I can make one now.

11:57.590 --> 11:58.950
Baskets for sale!

11:59.860 --> 12:01.590
Sachets! Trinkets!

12:21.260 --> 12:22.100
Welcome inside.

12:23.140 --> 12:24.126
Your wine. Please enjoy.

12:25.950 --> 12:26.830
Mr. Duan,

12:27.350 --> 12:28.830
you finally made it.

12:29.310 --> 12:30.230
Come.

12:30.230 --> 12:31.070
Mr. Wang.

12:31.780 --> 12:32.620
Miss Wang.

12:33.190 --> 12:34.216
Sorry to keep you waiting.

12:35.620 --> 12:36.470
I was wondering

12:36.660 --> 12:37.500
why Miss Wang would

12:37.500 --> 12:38.430
ask to meet here.

12:38.800 --> 12:39.660
So, it was you

12:39.660 --> 12:40.540
who chose this place.

12:41.500 --> 12:42.660
Bringing your sister here,

12:42.923 --> 12:44.196
are you trying to embarrass me?

12:44.860 --> 12:46.460
Mr. Duan, you jest.

12:47.310 --> 12:48.230
I heard

12:48.230 --> 12:50.070
you're a regular here.

12:50.430 --> 12:52.590
And Luoxian, the lady of this house,

12:53.140 --> 12:54.740
is your old acquaintance.

12:55.230 --> 12:57.620
Since you mean to get to know

12:57.780 --> 12:59.140
my sister better,

12:59.430 --> 13:00.740
it is only natural

13:00.950 --> 13:03.070
to bring her into your daily life.

13:03.710 --> 13:04.550
Besides,

13:05.070 --> 13:06.830
for men to seek pleasure

13:07.020 --> 13:08.310
is common enough at home.

13:08.620 --> 13:09.830
I understand you.

13:12.470 --> 13:13.620
And look at my sister.

13:13.900 --> 13:15.470
A noble lady, graceful and poised.

13:15.900 --> 13:17.140
Why would she mind

13:17.500 --> 13:18.990
your confidantes?

13:21.500 --> 13:23.110
What a pity, though.

13:23.310 --> 13:25.140
I have an appointment with Luoxian here.

13:25.990 --> 13:27.020
She is likely waiting

13:27.020 --> 13:28.350
quite anxiously by now.

13:31.070 --> 13:31.910
Mr. Duan,

13:32.860 --> 13:34.230
you must take good care

13:34.230 --> 13:35.110
of my sister.

13:35.430 --> 13:36.900
Of course.

13:39.590 --> 13:40.860
Luoxian.

13:44.430 --> 13:45.380
Since we parted,

13:46.230 --> 13:47.190
have you been well?

13:50.780 --> 13:52.020
Thank you for your concern.

13:52.470 --> 13:53.470
I've been quite well.

13:55.190 --> 13:56.470
In fact, you didn't wish

13:56.660 --> 13:57.620
to meet me here.

13:58.620 --> 14:00.430
- I...
- You said nothing to your brother,

14:00.830 --> 14:01.950
but you mind that men

14:02.356 --> 14:03.740
come here to seek pleasure, right?

14:04.620 --> 14:06.110
Mr. Duan,

14:06.376 --> 14:07.310
you're quite insightful.

14:07.470 --> 14:09.110
I admire it.

14:12.740 --> 14:15.230
But I can also sense

14:15.660 --> 14:16.500
that you do not seem

14:16.780 --> 14:18.500
so eager to know me,

14:18.780 --> 14:19.620
right?

14:32.020 --> 14:32.860
It's raining.

14:35.020 --> 14:35.860
Yes.

14:37.990 --> 14:38.950
A sudden summer rain.

14:44.540 --> 14:48.820
(Sugar Figurine)

15:34.380 --> 15:35.310
Who are you?

15:35.310 --> 15:36.470
What a scoundrel.

15:43.350 --> 15:44.710
You already forgot me?

15:47.900 --> 15:48.860
My name is Duan Xu,

15:50.493 --> 15:51.919
as in a supreme martial achievement.

15:53.613 --> 15:54.700
My courtesy name is Shunxi.

16:17.070 --> 16:17.910
He Simu.

16:28.350 --> 16:29.470
You recognized me,

16:30.230 --> 16:31.070
Foxy.

16:54.740 --> 16:55.950
How did you know it was me?

17:00.380 --> 17:01.990
Who else makes crow sugar figurines?

17:30.060 --> 17:30.990
You've come to Nandu.

17:39.020 --> 17:40.020
Why didn't you tell me?

17:42.990 --> 17:44.820
I came here on my own business.

17:45.630 --> 17:46.820
I didn't come here for you.

17:47.260 --> 17:48.190
Why would I tell you?

17:53.470 --> 17:54.630
So, you didn't plan to see me?

17:57.870 --> 17:59.260
Nandu is only so big.

17:59.710 --> 18:00.630
See? We met now.

18:01.670 --> 18:02.976
What a coincidence, General Duan.

18:03.300 --> 18:04.150
Why are you holding

18:04.150 --> 18:04.990
my friend?

18:07.500 --> 18:08.340
Prophet Hejia.

18:10.910 --> 18:11.910
Have you finished

18:12.100 --> 18:12.990
your official business?

18:19.150 --> 18:19.990
Great Ancestorظخ

18:22.470 --> 18:23.310
Miss He,

18:23.870 --> 18:25.150
why buy another sugar figurine?

18:25.670 --> 18:26.950
You can't even taste it.

18:27.350 --> 18:28.590
Yet you still like such things.

18:29.390 --> 18:30.740
Mind your own affairs.

18:31.740 --> 18:32.709
Your health is so poor,

18:32.720 --> 18:34.190
yet you chose a rainy day to roam.

18:34.500 --> 18:35.780
Have you lived long enough?

18:35.990 --> 18:36.830
I...

18:38.390 --> 18:40.100
We all have our quirks. Let it be.

18:41.910 --> 18:42.750
Let's go.

18:44.230 --> 18:45.070
Come on.

18:59.260 --> 19:00.100
Taste it for me.

19:00.430 --> 19:01.270
See if it's sweet.

19:13.150 --> 19:13.990
Here, take it.

19:16.280 --> 19:18.950
ظآزMemories trail like a shadowظآز

19:19.290 --> 19:24.800
ظآزScattered reflections
sink into my heartظآز

19:25.390 --> 19:31.400
ظآزIf I could softly call you like thisظآز

19:32.490 --> 19:37.100
ظآزAs gentle as a fleeting embraceظآز

19:38.600 --> 19:44.250
ظآزThough apart, my thoughts still swirlظآز

19:44.870 --> 19:50.490
ظآزA lifetime is given
for a name to be rememberedظآز

19:52.430 --> 19:53.470
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

19:54.580 --> 19:57.170
ظآزHope we'll experience them togetherظآز

19:57.190 --> 19:58.300
How did you know it was me?

19:59.260 --> 20:00.780
Who else makes crow sugar figurines?

20:01.870 --> 20:03.340
(Just now, she was so far away.)

20:04.260 --> 20:05.150
(I couldn't see)

20:05.150 --> 20:06.820
(what He Simu was holding,)

20:07.630 --> 20:08.670
(let alone make out)

20:08.670 --> 20:09.670
(a crow's shape.)

20:11.500 --> 20:12.340
(Exactly.)

20:14.150 --> 20:15.500
(How did I know it was her?)

20:16.190 --> 20:17.540
(How, in but a moment,)

20:18.430 --> 20:19.653
(among countless plain,)

20:19.664 --> 20:20.620
(strange mortal shells,)

20:21.580 --> 20:23.470
(I knew the soul within.)

20:23.670 --> 20:24.910
I'm the Sovereign

20:25.820 --> 20:27.230
of Spirits.

20:29.060 --> 20:30.340
(I have only known this soul)

20:30.780 --> 20:31.870
(for less than half a year.)

20:33.100 --> 20:34.260
(Everyone says)

20:35.230 --> 20:36.070
(forgetting)

20:36.540 --> 20:37.390
(is something)

20:37.390 --> 20:38.540
(exceedingly easy to do.)

20:39.870 --> 20:41.630
(Perhaps one day, when my temples gray)

20:42.780 --> 20:44.280
(and I reach the age Father spoke of)

20:44.740 --> 20:46.500
(when childhood bonds fade from mind,)

20:47.470 --> 20:49.060
(will I still, in the vast crowd,)

20:49.780 --> 20:51.060
(recognize her at a glance?)

20:54.300 --> 20:55.630
(By the time that day comes,)

20:56.670 --> 20:57.950
(even if I recognize her,)

20:59.430 --> 21:00.500
(will I still, like today,)

21:00.500 --> 21:01.870
(run after her without a thought?)

21:04.670 --> 21:07.880
ظآزThere are passions and painsظآز

21:08.260 --> 21:10.950
ظآزHope we'll experience them togetherظآز

21:11.780 --> 21:12.710
(She's the first girl)

21:12.710 --> 21:13.670
(I fell for,)

21:15.670 --> 21:16.520
(the first girl)

21:16.530 --> 21:17.670
(to awaken me,)

21:18.910 --> 21:20.040
ظآزGrows dim and fades awayظآز

21:20.060 --> 21:20.950
(the first girl)

21:21.710 --> 21:22.950
(who came)

21:22.950 --> 21:23.790
(for me)

21:24.670 --> 21:25.870
(in that pitch-black darkness,)

21:28.390 --> 21:29.630
(the first girl)

21:30.710 --> 21:32.260
(who feels the world's beauty)

21:32.260 --> 21:33.430
(and pain because of me,)

21:33.430 --> 21:35.930
ظآزWorth more than any barren landظآز

21:36.190 --> 21:38.670
ظآزI might as well
spend the rest of my lifeظآز

21:40.060 --> 21:41.710
(and the girl who always calls me Foxy)

21:42.780 --> 21:43.990
(and says, "I'll protect you,")

21:44.470 --> 21:46.390
("but do not love me.")

21:46.950 --> 21:48.870
But I am the wish you can't fulfill.

21:49.910 --> 21:51.060
Take me out

21:51.060 --> 21:51.900
of your wishes.

21:52.530 --> 21:55.000
ظآزA dream I'm lost inظآز

21:55.150 --> 21:56.470
(How ironic.)

21:57.990 --> 21:58.870
(My original wish)

21:58.870 --> 22:00.190
(was to live as an ordinary man,)

22:01.430 --> 22:02.910
(free of the All-Knowing's shadow,)

22:03.390 --> 22:05.300
(and learn to live like everyone else.)

22:06.100 --> 22:07.910
(I tried so hard to do that.)

22:08.540 --> 22:09.390
(But now,)

22:09.740 --> 22:10.820
(everything has gone)

22:10.820 --> 22:11.740
(the opposite way)

22:12.540 --> 22:13.580
(from my original wish.)

22:16.990 --> 22:18.190
(He Simu)

22:18.950 --> 22:20.540
(has become my new wish,)

22:21.710 --> 22:23.540
(the most shocking wish of all.)

22:30.470 --> 22:31.630
(I will have no one)

22:32.430 --> 22:33.780
(but He Simu.)

22:42.990 --> 22:44.150
Hejia Fengyi,

22:45.710 --> 22:46.740
your gift for divination

22:46.740 --> 22:48.100
has truly grown by the day.

22:49.910 --> 22:51.780
You asked me out only for this moment?

22:53.710 --> 22:55.300
What a coincidence.

22:55.910 --> 22:57.340
Who knew we'd run into him?

23:10.780 --> 23:12.540
How has Duan Shunxi been lately?

23:14.260 --> 23:15.150
Probably not well.

23:16.260 --> 23:17.870
After he returned from the battlefield,

23:18.033 --> 23:19.379
his military command was stripped.

23:19.470 --> 23:20.870
He was given an idle post,

23:21.060 --> 23:22.390
doing nothing.

23:23.060 --> 23:23.910
Maybe he was hurt

23:23.910 --> 23:25.100
on the battlefield.

23:25.340 --> 23:26.580
He looks somewhat weak.

23:27.150 --> 23:28.950
Drenched in rain in this weather,

23:29.100 --> 23:30.670
he may well fall ill.

23:30.990 --> 23:32.870
As for falling ill, I know it well.

23:33.100 --> 23:34.540
Once men like him, who usually seem

23:34.540 --> 23:35.540
so strong and healthy,

23:35.540 --> 23:36.390
fall ill,

23:36.390 --> 23:37.870
it can hit like a mountain collapsing.

23:37.870 --> 23:39.020
It'll be perilous.

23:39.150 --> 23:40.990
One lapse, and a small ailment grows.

23:40.990 --> 23:41.830
Then a life is lost.

23:44.430 --> 23:45.430
If you talk less,

23:45.430 --> 23:46.780
will your whole body ache?

23:47.910 --> 23:49.150
Yeah.

23:49.780 --> 23:51.820
Great Ancestor, you know me best.

23:52.580 --> 23:53.420
Are you afraid

23:54.020 --> 23:55.020
my words will doom him?

23:55.870 --> 23:56.710
Easy, easy.

23:56.710 --> 23:58.060
I didn't use spells just now.

23:58.340 --> 23:59.300
And even if I had,

23:59.300 --> 24:00.140
it'd only be to pray

24:01.430 --> 24:02.270
for his well-being.

24:05.710 --> 24:06.580
I know.

24:07.540 --> 24:08.430
You know?

24:09.150 --> 24:11.710
So, you simply care for him

24:12.190 --> 24:13.820
and can't bear hearing him die?

24:16.950 --> 24:17.990
If you're unwell,

24:18.190 --> 24:19.500
speak a little less.

24:21.820 --> 24:23.670
How are you anything like Aunt?

24:25.430 --> 24:26.820
Perhaps

24:27.763 --> 24:28.710
I'm as pretty as she is.

24:32.780 --> 24:33.670
Great Ancestor,

24:34.340 --> 24:35.300
you asked me before

24:35.300 --> 24:36.780
how mortals live in the Void.

24:37.060 --> 24:37.950
I almost thought

24:37.950 --> 24:39.230
he had become your beloved.

24:39.596 --> 24:40.710
But after Duan Xu returned,

24:40.710 --> 24:41.550
I could see

24:42.300 --> 24:43.150
his resentment

24:43.340 --> 24:44.400
was heavier than spirits'.

24:44.900 --> 24:45.740
I had assumed

24:45.740 --> 24:46.870
he was frustrated in court.

24:47.150 --> 24:47.990
But then,

24:47.990 --> 24:49.420
seeing how he grabbed you,

24:49.670 --> 24:50.740
I finally understood.

24:50.870 --> 24:52.820
It spelled out three clear words.

24:53.340 --> 24:55.150
Troubled by romance.

25:00.190 --> 25:01.205
Count yourself fortunate

25:01.216 --> 25:02.340
to be here now.

25:04.150 --> 25:05.150
That saved your life.

25:06.670 --> 25:07.870
Great Ancestor, forgive me.

25:08.470 --> 25:09.500
I saw how calm

25:09.630 --> 25:10.740
you were just now.

25:10.910 --> 25:12.230
I take it you've turned him down.

25:12.430 --> 25:14.060
So, it has nothing to do with you.

25:14.470 --> 25:15.950
I think he and Miss Wang

25:15.950 --> 25:17.260
are getting along well.

25:17.260 --> 25:18.630
They're probably in love.

25:18.820 --> 25:20.300
Maybe he'll soon forget

25:20.300 --> 25:21.300
the 400-year-old youظخ

25:25.300 --> 25:26.740
a seasoned woman like you,

25:27.500 --> 25:30.020
and turn to a fair beauty instead.

25:35.540 --> 25:36.630
Great Ancestor.

25:37.230 --> 25:38.190
Great Ancestor,

25:38.390 --> 25:40.150
you have to hear the truth sometimes.

25:40.540 --> 25:42.060
How was any of that the truth?

25:42.580 --> 25:43.710
How was that not the truth?

25:43.710 --> 25:45.230
Aren't you over 400 years old?

25:45.630 --> 25:47.390
They were distant and polite.

25:47.630 --> 25:49.020
But you called me over

25:49.020 --> 25:50.540
to stir things up and twist the truth.

25:50.990 --> 25:52.500
Who taught you to wag your tongue?

25:55.820 --> 25:58.100
They are not in love at all.

25:58.670 --> 25:59.510
I see.

25:59.670 --> 26:01.390
That's the real point here.

26:06.540 --> 26:08.540
But Great Ancestor, don't forget.

26:08.990 --> 26:09.830
She's the one

26:10.190 --> 26:12.430
Duan Xu proposed to.

26:21.390 --> 26:23.230
You do have a silver tongue.

26:24.710 --> 26:25.456
Have you finished

26:25.467 --> 26:26.470
the task I assigned you?

26:27.190 --> 26:28.430
Have you caught Song Xingyu?

26:30.260 --> 26:31.100
Rest assured.

26:31.630 --> 26:32.740
I've already been screening

26:32.740 --> 26:33.990
those you've left marks on.

26:34.870 --> 26:35.710
But, Great Ancestor,

26:35.710 --> 26:37.430
you know the state of my health.

26:37.670 --> 26:39.710
We must wait for an auspicious day.

26:39.910 --> 26:40.750
Otherwise,

26:41.870 --> 26:43.039
the little life I have left

26:43.050 --> 26:43.870
will be worn down.

26:44.260 --> 26:45.340
What if my health

26:45.340 --> 26:46.300
is harmed?

26:53.060 --> 26:55.100
A bustling place like Nandu

26:55.300 --> 26:57.060
is full of splendor and temptation,

26:57.870 --> 26:59.060
yet as far as the eye can see,

26:59.340 --> 27:01.190
there's no spiritual aura or spirits.

27:01.780 --> 27:02.620
Is Song Xingyu

27:03.500 --> 27:04.990
behind this too?

27:09.190 --> 27:10.870
I'll give you the obsessions tomorrow.

27:11.060 --> 27:12.150
Let's call it a day.

27:14.870 --> 27:15.710
Great Ancestor,

27:16.150 --> 27:17.430
where do you actually stay?

27:18.060 --> 27:19.500
Come find me tomorrow night.

27:21.740 --> 27:23.580
Where am I supposed to find you?

27:31.630 --> 27:32.470
Xu.

27:35.230 --> 27:36.133
With an umbrella,

27:36.144 --> 27:37.340
how did you get so drenched?

27:38.190 --> 27:39.030
I didn't use it.

27:40.060 --> 27:41.630
You didn't use it in the pouring rain?

27:42.260 --> 27:43.470
What if you fall ill?

27:44.100 --> 27:45.060
Why are you so careless

27:45.060 --> 27:46.060
with your own health?

27:48.710 --> 27:49.550
Exactly.

27:51.190 --> 27:53.230
I knew I should use an umbrella,

27:54.020 --> 27:54.860
yet I didn't.

27:55.990 --> 27:57.670
I knew I should live well,

27:58.710 --> 28:00.190
yet I refused.

28:02.060 --> 28:02.910
What a madman.

28:04.500 --> 28:05.340
Xu,

28:07.150 --> 28:08.340
is something wrong?

28:15.500 --> 28:16.630
I've fallen for a young lady.

28:21.500 --> 28:22.990
Is she a lady from Nandu?

28:25.500 --> 28:26.630
She is not from Nandu.

28:29.100 --> 28:30.390
You met her on the battlefield?

28:32.060 --> 28:33.230
She didn't come back with you?

28:35.190 --> 28:36.740
She's the only girl in a good family.

28:37.630 --> 28:38.820
If I were to be with her,

28:39.576 --> 28:40.929
I'd have to marry into her family.

28:47.230 --> 28:48.070
Then,

28:48.390 --> 28:49.230
does she

28:49.470 --> 28:50.670
like you?

28:53.020 --> 28:53.950
She turned me down.

28:55.260 --> 28:56.150
In her eyes,

28:56.540 --> 28:58.020
let alone the Duan clan of Nandu,

28:58.470 --> 28:59.910
even Great Liang, or the whole world,

29:00.500 --> 29:01.500
means nothing at all.

29:03.990 --> 29:05.870
What kind of lady is she?

29:06.630 --> 29:08.260
A lady unlike any in this world.

29:23.560 --> 29:24.800
- Xu.
- You wanted me?

29:25.580 --> 29:26.710
Your friends are here.

29:26.710 --> 29:28.500
I've seated them in the hall with tea.

29:28.870 --> 29:29.710
All right.

29:30.740 --> 29:31.580
Jingyuan,

29:32.910 --> 29:34.230
have you had dealings

29:34.360 --> 29:36.006
with the wife
of the Minister of Revenue?

29:38.300 --> 29:39.470
I've crossed paths

29:39.630 --> 29:41.300
with Mrs. Wang.

29:41.710 --> 29:42.550
We're on fair terms.

29:42.910 --> 29:43.750
Why?

29:44.150 --> 29:45.020
Today, Mr. Wang

29:45.340 --> 29:46.780
asked me to take Miss Wang home.

29:47.500 --> 29:48.820
While I was talking with her,

29:48.950 --> 29:50.550
I spotted a familiar face on the street.

29:51.020 --> 29:52.100
They might be Chong spies,

29:52.260 --> 29:53.150
so I went after them,

29:53.740 --> 29:54.870
neglected Miss Wang,

29:55.430 --> 29:56.740
and failed to escort her home.

29:59.260 --> 30:00.233
All right, I understand.

30:00.500 --> 30:01.820
I'll go visit Mrs. Wang at once

30:01.820 --> 30:02.870
and apologize for you.

30:05.340 --> 30:06.260
Wait, Xu.

30:07.470 --> 30:09.540
Don't you already fancy someone?

30:09.950 --> 30:11.260
What do you plan

30:11.780 --> 30:12.910
to do with Miss Wang?

30:13.910 --> 30:14.750
Do not worry.

30:15.300 --> 30:16.140
I have my own plan.

30:37.540 --> 30:38.390
What brings you here?

30:39.740 --> 30:40.580
Xu.

30:41.470 --> 30:42.310
Take a look.

30:42.500 --> 30:43.740
Wu Shengliu asked us

30:43.740 --> 30:44.820
to bring this to you.

30:45.740 --> 30:47.190
Though the war has settled,

30:47.540 --> 30:49.300
the border still sees unrest.

30:50.020 --> 30:51.202
This was supposed to be a gift

30:51.213 --> 30:52.670
for your promotion.

30:53.260 --> 30:54.470
But he never expected

30:54.583 --> 30:55.649
how things would turn out.

30:57.740 --> 30:58.580
Judging by the style,

30:59.843 --> 31:01.196
it belongs to at least a general.

31:02.500 --> 31:04.580
Wu Shengliu did well.

31:06.670 --> 31:07.510
Xu,

31:08.060 --> 31:09.870
are we staying in Nandu for good?

31:11.910 --> 31:12.750
What I want

31:13.390 --> 31:14.412
has always been to reclaim

31:14.423 --> 31:15.150
the 17 Prefectures

31:15.740 --> 31:16.866
and have peace for the realm

31:17.060 --> 31:17.900
and the people.

31:18.470 --> 31:19.580
Great Liang seeks no war,

31:20.260 --> 31:22.020
but North Chong still covets our land.

31:22.630 --> 31:23.563
Once they get a chance,

31:23.693 --> 31:24.743
they'll surely strike back.

31:24.950 --> 31:26.100
We must prepare in advance.

31:26.540 --> 31:27.710
Then, when do we leave?

31:29.980 --> 31:31.870
I can't stay in Nandu another day.

31:32.340 --> 31:34.390
I am stuck indoors, learning embroidery

31:34.630 --> 31:35.950
and having blind dates.

31:36.820 --> 31:37.660
If this keeps going,

31:37.670 --> 31:38.770
I won't even lift my blade.

31:39.540 --> 31:41.260
I have been idle in Nandu as well.

31:41.260 --> 31:42.100
Right?

31:46.150 --> 31:47.580
Yunzhou and Luozhou are back,

31:48.580 --> 31:49.540
but Yunzhou's steeds

31:50.390 --> 31:51.230
have yet to thunder

31:51.240 --> 31:52.430
across the battlefield.

31:53.150 --> 31:54.150
Luozhou's Tianluo Ore

31:54.910 --> 31:56.580
has yet to arm our men.

31:57.060 --> 31:57.900
Some matters

31:58.390 --> 31:59.390
must be settled in Nandu.

32:00.340 --> 32:01.190
(Yuzao Pleasure House)

32:01.190 --> 32:02.300
This way, please.

32:02.630 --> 32:03.470
I'm telling you.

32:03.470 --> 32:04.540
Take care.

32:04.540 --> 32:06.430
I'll be coming back to find you.

32:07.180 --> 32:08.020
Ah, you're here.

32:08.020 --> 32:08.910
This way, please.

32:08.910 --> 32:10.150
Mr. Zhang, you're.

32:10.150 --> 32:11.300
Yuzao Pleasure House.

32:13.340 --> 32:14.180
Take care.

32:14.690 --> 32:15.540
Come again next time.

32:15.540 --> 32:17.390
Great Ancestor
surely knows how to have fun.

32:18.390 --> 32:19.780
She became the top beauty.

32:21.780 --> 32:22.780
Please head inside.

32:22.780 --> 32:23.620
Sure thing.

32:28.870 --> 32:32.820
Alright, alright.

32:33.740 --> 32:35.020
You've finished a whole jar.

32:37.190 --> 32:38.030
All right.

32:48.300 --> 32:49.390
Why hasn't it reached

32:49.390 --> 32:50.870
closing time?

32:59.230 --> 33:00.390
Heavens,

33:01.500 --> 33:02.870
I must have slept in too late.

33:03.740 --> 33:04.680
I even saw the Prophet

33:04.710 --> 33:05.710
come here for amusement.

33:15.990 --> 33:16.830
Great Ancestor.

33:18.060 --> 33:18.900
Great Ancestorظخ

33:27.910 --> 33:28.750
Fine wine,

33:29.820 --> 33:30.660
beauties,

33:33.780 --> 33:34.990
tales of desire,

33:36.390 --> 33:37.740
and obsessions at their peak.

33:38.300 --> 33:39.580
Good for you, Great Ancestor.

33:41.300 --> 33:42.300
See if it's enough.

33:49.710 --> 33:50.990
I need a little more.

33:51.500 --> 33:52.340
Great Ancestor,

33:52.540 --> 33:53.580
have you ever thought

33:53.630 --> 33:55.176
what the magical artifact will be like?

34:17.480 --> 34:18.540
(In Yuzao Pleasure House,)

34:18.750 --> 34:20.550
(the Prophet secretly meets Miss He.)

34:43.350 --> 34:44.190
Sir,

34:44.580 --> 34:45.700
please go upstairs.

34:52.830 --> 34:53.670
You should leave now.

34:59.220 --> 35:00.060
A spirit is here.

35:00.470 --> 35:02.020
A guest has arrived.

35:02.990 --> 35:03.830
Great Ancestor,

35:04.180 --> 35:05.020
something is wrong.

35:05.950 --> 35:06.790
This spiritual energy

35:07.390 --> 35:08.230
is very strong.

35:10.910 --> 35:11.910
I'll get you out of here.

35:41.180 --> 35:42.270
Greetings, sir.

35:43.310 --> 35:44.220
May I ask

35:44.220 --> 35:45.390
what story you wish to tell?

35:48.270 --> 35:49.220
The story begins

35:49.220 --> 35:51.310
with a loyal prince.

35:52.580 --> 35:53.870
He was promoted young.

35:54.140 --> 35:55.350
He basked in imperial favor.

35:56.270 --> 35:57.910
The court and the realm all believed

35:58.100 --> 35:59.350
he would inherit the throne.

35:59.990 --> 36:01.580
Yet history always leaves regrets.

36:02.140 --> 36:04.430
His younger brother saw no hope
to vie for the heirship,

36:05.140 --> 36:06.350
so he started a rebellion.

36:07.220 --> 36:09.350
The prince was bound by kinship,

36:10.830 --> 36:12.470
never knowing

36:12.830 --> 36:14.580
it was a deadly trap

36:15.020 --> 36:16.180
tailored just for him.

36:18.060 --> 36:19.580
His brother framed him.

36:20.270 --> 36:21.430
That loyal prince

36:22.100 --> 36:24.580
suddenly became a rebel.

36:26.790 --> 36:27.660
My Lady,

36:29.430 --> 36:31.020
do you know how the prince

36:31.500 --> 36:32.700
met his end at last?

36:36.950 --> 36:37.790
Yan,

36:40.390 --> 36:41.390
stop fooling around.

